      <conbody class="- topic/body  concept/conbody ">
         <p outputclass="List1" class="- topic/p ">(a) Individual nonavailability determinations.</p>
         <p outputclass="List2" class="- topic/p ">(2) Contracting officers may use the following template for individual nonavailability determinations under this section:</p>
         <p class="- topic/p ">SUBJECT: Individual Nonavailability Determination Exception under DFARS <xref href="225.7018-4.dita"
                  outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
